  "texts": [
    "Use electronic voice synthesis devices to help the patient express themselves 4.",
    "Try music therapy, especially melodic intonation therapy 5.",
    "If possible, try physical therapies such as transcranial direct current stimulation (tDCS) 6.",
    "Drug therapy and acupuncture may also be helpful.",
    "Please proceed under the guidance of a doctor 1."
  ]
